		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Just using Pro Motion.<br />Pro Motion doesn't enforce restrictions. It does have a colour constraint checking feature, but mostly just do it by eye.<br />So quite possibly a few minor restriction breaking errors, tile counts are probably a bit high too, but should be adaptable to the real thing with few tweaks.

		

		</td>
